<p>That's all there is to it. After that, you are ready to start shopping!</p>
<p style="font-size:11px;color:#999;">
If the above link does not work, type in or copy and paste this link into your Web browser: <br />
<%= link_to url, url %>
</p>
<br />
Thank you for registering!
